| Role                 | Color                         | Usage                     |
| -------------------- | ----------------------------- | ------------------------- |
| **Background**       | `#0f0c29 → #302b63 → #24243e` | Main page gradient        |
| **Primary Accent**   | `#06b6d4` (Cyan)              | Buttons, glow, hover      |
| **Secondary Accent** | `#a855f7` (Purple)            | Highlights, text gradient |
| **Card Glass**       | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)`      | Glassmorphism backgrounds |
| **Border Glow**      | `#22d3ee` (Cyan glow shadow)  | Subtle glow under cards   |
| **Text**             | `#ffffff` / `#d1d5db`         | White and muted grey text |
